dml.team5.antlr

Interface ModifiedPLSQLListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ModifiedPLSQLBaseListener

    public interface ModifiedPLSQLListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by ModifiedPLSQLParser.
